body:
All honesty I think ADcs need a buff for this mode, compared to everyone else they are the only role that cannot keep up in this game mode, so far from what I can see it hasn&#039;t been improved too much since the first time it came out. If you cannot still have fun with /EVERY/ Champion; with out being insta-killed by the top 10 picks in this mode, than where is this going?

It&#039;s just a mode to pick the most douche-bag champion. There is no fun for both sides, literally one-sided soon as one team gets a lead.

IMO Worst Game Mode. 1/10 {{item:3070}}
